  "title": "📌 Patient Service Associate (PSA) #HHLT",
  "description": "<p><br />📌 <strong>Patient Service Associate (PSA)</strong><br />📝 <strong>1-Year Contract</strong></p><h3>📍 <strong>Work Location</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Bedok, Outram</strong><br /></p></li></ul><h3>⏰ <strong>Working Hours (44 hrs/week)</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Weekdays:</strong> 6.30am – 7.00pm</p></li><li><p><strong>Saturday:</strong> 6.30am – 1.30pm<br /><br /></p></li></ul><h3>🧠 <strong>Job Scope</strong></h3><p>Greet and register patients</p><p>Schedule appointments and coordinate specialist referrals</p><p>Handle payments and attend to patient enquiries professionally</p><p>Manage patient concerns and escalate when necessary</p><p>Provide quality customer service and clear communication</p><p>Assist at <strong>Health Monitoring Station</strong> (taking height, weight & blood pressure) based on roster<br /><br /><br /><br />🎓 <strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum NITEC/Diploma</li></ul><ul><li><p>No healthcare experience required</p></li><li><p>Prior customer service / admin experience is beneficial</p></li><li><p>Comfortable using computer systems (registration, appointments, payments)</p></li><li><p>Service-oriented with good communication skills<br /></p><p><br />If interested, please email me at biopharma@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p></p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)</p></li></ul>",
